                <note rend="inline" type="source">791.003/76: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Persia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Philip</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-03-05T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 5, 1928—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>18. Your 21, March 5, 11 a.m., paragraph (4). The Department presumes you were
                    referring to political aims of Great Britain and that you approve cooperation
                    with the British on a basis of the 16 safeguards to protect foreigners in Persia
                    following abrogation of the treaties. Please cable a reply.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
